biography: New Street Adventure was an English band led by Nick Corbin. The band comprised Nick Corbin (lead vocals and guitar), Billy Farr (lead guitar), Ashley Hayden (bass guitar), Charlie Myers (keys and synth), Ollie Futcher (Drums), Carmy Love and Emma Noble (backing vocals). The band released their debut album in 2014. Read more on Last.fm. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply.
